Package fr.internetcartographier.model.geolocationservice

Class GeolocationData.TypedGeolocationData

java.lang.Object
fr.internetcartographier.model.geolocationservice.GeolocationData.TypedGeolocationData
Enclosing class:
GeolocationData
public static class GeolocationData.TypedGeolocationData extends Object
A nested class representing typed geolocation data, including the service generating the data and an optional GeolocationData object. Serving to know which geolocation service has generated the geo data.
